[src:adams-run-south-carolina/2020-united-states-census] Census Bureau issued another press release announcing 2020 census field operations would be suspended for an additional two weeks, through April 15, 2020.
[src:adams-run-south-carolina/2020-united-states-census] The agency announced on April 10, 2020, that it took steps to make "more employees available to respond to requests" at the call centers.
